== 早年生活 ==
孫承完於1994年2月21日出生於[[韓國|韓國]][[首爾特別市|首爾特別市]][[城北區|城北區]]城北洞，屬於首爾高尚半山住宅區，當時就讀堤川中心小學。因姐姐孫勝希（音譯）的關係，小學5年級時便獨自留學在[[加拿大|加拿大]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kim|first1=Bo-ra|title='문제적남자' 웬디, SM 뇌섹녀..'올A 성적+4개국어'|url=http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2016/09/04/2016090402165.html|accessdate=September 9, 2016|work=Chosun|date=September 4, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905131848/http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2016/09/04/2016090402165.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Fate|first1=Kay|title='Dolly' set to open at Shattuck|url=http://www.southernminn.com/faribault_daily_news/archives/article_772e1271-00aa-559c-8d88-2d3a3d2f321c.html|accessdate=October 16, 2014|work=Faribault Daily News|date=February 17, 2010|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704055453/http://www.southernminn.com/faribault_daily_news/archives/article_772e1271-00aa-559c-8d88-2d3a3d2f321c.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite episode |accessdate=April 22, 2015 |series=Gayo Plaza |author=Kim Sung-joo |network=[[Korean_Broadcasting_System|KBS]] |station=KBS Cool FM ||date=April 10, 2015 |language=ko}}</ref>，之后孫承完的家人從韓國移民至[[加拿大|加拿大]]的[[多倫多|多倫多]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://redvelvet.smtown.com/profile|title=Red Velvet Profile|accessdate=October 11, 2014|language=ko|archive-date=2014-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018195600/http://redvelvet.smtown.com/profile|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite episode |accessdate=April 9, 2015 |series=Cultwo Show |author=Jung Chan-woo, Kim Tae-gyun |network=[[Seoul_Broadcasting_System|SBS]] |station=SBS Power FM |date=April 9, 2015 |language=ko}}</ref>由於家人都是喜愛音樂，孫承完從5歲時就有要當[[歌手|歌手]]的夢想。<ref name="tablo">{{Cite episode |episodelink= |url= |accessdate= |series=Tablo Dreaming Radio |author=[[Tablo|Tablo]] |network=[[Munhwa_Broadcasting_Corporation|MBC]] |station=HLKV-FM |date=October 14, 2015 |began= |ended= |season= |seriesno= |number= |minutes= |time= |language=ko}}</ref>除了